            <title>[SPARK-3891] Support Hive Percentile UDAF with array of percentile values</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-3891</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Spark PR 2620 brings in the support of Hive percentile UDAF.&lt;br/&gt;
